meta {
  name: List Run Files
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{base_url}}/runs/{{run_id}}/files
}

docs {
  Lists all files in the run's workspace directory, organized by subdirectory.

  Subdirectories include: rawdata, cutPrimer, bwa, fastqc, bam2bed,
  bed2peak, readlen, logs. Each file entry includes name, relative path,
  size in bytes, and modification timestamp.

  Prerequisites:
  - Run must exist with a workspace directory
  - Set run_id environment variable to the target run

  Expected response: 200 OK
  {
    "files": {
      "rawdata": [{"name": "R1.fastq.gz", "path": "rawdata/R1.fastq.gz", "size": 12345, "modified": 1705000000}],
      "cutPrimer": [...],
      "bwa": [...]
    }
  }

  Use the "path" values from this response with "Download File" to
  retrieve specific files.
}
